<br>
If I have 1000 AC, does that mean that adding 200 AC to take me up to the "softcap" will allow me to tank an orc pawn better? Or would my average damage taken remain basically the same?<br>
<br>
If I only had 600 AC, would adding another 100 AC make me take less average damage from that orc pawn? If not, does that mean that the softcap is 600 AC?<br>
<br>
Another question...<br>
<br>
If I have 600 AC, would increasing my ac by 25% (150 AC) reduce my average damage by 25% when tanking a flurry drake? Would it have a noticeable effect at all on my average damage taken? If not, does that mean 600 AC is the softcap? <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=14686">Graal MacBladefury</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
