<br>
-- tier 1 exp grind PoP mobs have relatively low ATK values, hence mitigation matters more here than in SoV/SoL.<br>
<br>
-- different mobs &quot;cap out&quot; vs their opponents ac at different levels. in other words, above 900 ac, there is no improvement when fighting SolB kobolds. however, if fighting Kael arena giants, AC up to 1250 or so continues to offer increased protection.<br>
