im curious, Brutul, do you disagree with the above, or did i misunderstand you? <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
I'm not saying anything with regard to the AC soft cap.  All I'm saying is that Daxos posting fairly dubious theories and speculation and representing it as proven fact is irresponsible.  That sort of post is exactly what causes much of the misinformation on these forums.  <br>
<br>
What you posted above is a plausible theory and may very well be true, but I have seen no convincing evidence that it is, and posting rumors and old wive's tales as unquestionable fact is bad for the board and the community.<br>
<br>
I have my own theories on the effectiveness of AC, and they are pretty much in line with the average posters on this board.  I would not be so arrogant as to present them as fact however, and that is what I was criticizing Draxos for. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6629">Brutul Vilesilencer</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
